# AJX Technologies Website - System Design Document

## 1. Executive Summary
This document outlines the system architecture for the AJX Technologies website. The application is a modern, high-performance web platform built using **Next.js 15 (App Router)** and **React 19**. It serves as both a public-facing corporate portfolio and contains an internal administrative CMS for content management.

## 2. High-Level Architecture
The system follows a **Monolithic Architecture** leveraging the "Full Stack" capabilities of Next.js.

*   **Frontend**: Server-Side Rendered (SSR) and Client-Side Rendered (CSR) React components.
*   **Backend**: Next.js API Routes (Serverless functions) handling business logic and database interactions.
*   **Database**: MongoDB, accessed directly via the native Node.js driver.
*   **Authentication**: NextAuth.js (v5) handling session management and protection for Admin routes.

